{"tid":456064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最佳航空公司排名出爐　國泰航空由第4位大跌至第9位","createTime":"2017-11-02T15:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T17:16:52.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"73dd357ef035b85c425dcf6087be885b3055c836","tid":456064,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://網站AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99AirlineRatings.com&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1dcced43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網站AirlineRatings.com</a>今（2日）公布2018年10大最佳航空公司排名，本港的國泰航空下跌5位急挫至第9位；而頭三位順次序分別是，新西蘭航空、澳洲航空，以及新加坡航空。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f33c2a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>自2013年起公布全球「最佳航空公司」排名，國泰航空以往亦曾位列三甲，但去年卻跌至第4，今年更大跌至第9位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f33c2a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>主要是以包括航空公司的安全紀錄、乘客對航空公司的評價、機齡等因素來評核航空公司；今年的榜首是連續5年、被評為最佳航空公司的新西蘭航空，第二位是澳洲航空，第三位則是新加坡航空。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f33c2a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>解釋，三甲的航空公司都因為購買了最新型的波音787和空中巴士A350，因而得到大大的加分。<br />\n<br />\n2018年10大最佳航空公司排名<br />\n排名<br />\n航空公司<br />\n1<br />\n新西蘭航空（Air New Zealand）<br />\n2<br />\n澳洲航空（Qantas Airways）<br />\n3<br />\n新加坡航空（Singapore Airlines）<br />\n4<br />\n維珍澳洲航空（Virgin Australia）<br />\n5<br />\n維珍航空（Virgin Atlantic）<br />\n6<br />\n阿堤哈德航空（Etihad Airways）<br />\n7<br />\n全日空（All Nippon Airways）<br />\n8<br />\n大韓航空（Korean Air）<br />\n9<br />\n國泰航空（Cathay Pacific）<br />\n10<br />\n日航（Japan Airlines）"},{"pid":"3bc1f5900d05686102219e4bf2edff8705e29bfb","tid":456064,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"腥港豬只會拎排第一既榜嚟打飛機<br />\n<br />\n依啲第九既   無視不解釋"},{"pid":"ec48c971d2e37f02ff8c130db4ec389ac34d3c4e","tid":456064,"uid":14816,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"百份報聽日頭版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ff24dbac0d68d7a935a4f8b3c6d56eaea51c73","tid":456064,"uid":1099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"因航唔係買左a350咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fb2373802aa6f0beb7ee93df4697c23613c4cc","tid":456064,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"因"},{"pid":"3339913c590c5be543c82b5a276e9e2736a42cef","tid":456064,"uid":31962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"炒油變炒魷，公司內人心一早已失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得閒睇下CX secret 就覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bba688966ad02172765e2a00cb35da38a753d6f","tid":456064,"uid":15320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"QR呢EK呢<br />\n<br />\nVA都上榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04f28d97ff043b29ca24b208ec8ac27d4ca2a38","tid":456064,"uid":134226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"[quote]因航唔係買左a350咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote<br />\n正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7297802feee717ece616392fb17b23310edf3a","tid":456064,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15: